# Agent Hub — Project Registry
# Format: path:DisplayName
# One project per line. Comments and blank lines are ignored.
# The path must be absolute or start with ~ (which expands to $HOME).
#
# Add your projects here after running setup.sh.
# Then run: bootstrap-project.sh <path> to wire each one into the brain.
#
# Examples:
#   ~/my-saas:MySaaS
#   ~/side-project:SideProject
#   ~/client-work/acme:AcmeApp
